-760","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":5243,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/16\/tibb-every-disease-has-cure\/","url_meta":{"origin":27280,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Allah created a cure for every disease","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 16, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah did not send down any disease but that he also sent its cure.\" In another narration, the Prophet said, \"One who has knowledge of it knows it, and one ignorant of it is ignorant.\"\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26810,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/09\/27\/medicine-hot-sweet-drinks\/","url_meta":{"origin":27280,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Hot, sweet, healthy drinks bring comfort","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 27, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, talbina rests the heart of a sick person and takes away some grief.\" Source:\u00a0S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5365 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari Ibn Hajar said, \"Al-Asma'i said talbina is a broth made from flour or bran,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32706,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/07\/all-cures-but-aging\/","url_meta":{"origin":27280,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Medicine: Allah placed cures for all diseases, except aging","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Usamah ibn Sharik reported: A bedouin said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, shall we not seek treatment?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYes, O servants of Allah, seek treatment. Verily, Allah did not place a disease but that he also placed its treatment or cure, except for one ailment.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20922,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/09\/17\/shafii-science-religion-world-medicine\/","url_meta":{"origin":27280,"position":3},"title":"Shafi\u2019i on Knowledge: Learn sciences of the religion and world","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abi Hatim reported: Al-Shafi\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cVerily, knowledge is only two types: knowledge of the religion and knowledge of the world. The knowledge of religion is to achieve juristic understanding (fiqh) and the knowledge of the world is medicine. Do not settle in a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35724,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/20\/quran-honey\/","url_meta":{"origin":27280,"position":4},"title":"Abdullah on Medicine: Use the Quran and honey for healing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 20, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Ahwas reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cYou must make use of two healers: the Quran and honey.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 2345 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Bayhaqi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0635\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d \u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u0628\u0650\u0627\u0644\u0634\u0651\u0650\u0641\u064e\u0627\u0626\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064f\u0631\u0652\u0622\u0646\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14646,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/08\/worldly-causes-qada-wal-qadr\/","url_meta":{"origin":27280,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Qadr: Worldly causes are pat of Allah\u2019s decree","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ya'mar al-'Uthri reported: I asked, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, the incantations we use, the medicines which heal us, and our fortifications against the enemy; do they repel anything from the decree of Allah?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThey are part of the decree of Allah.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","